OL,3,CThe mum tackling knife-crime in
OL,4,Ccommunities after brother's murder
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports journalist and
OL,7,Fpresenter Zoe Muldoon met Laura Hughes
OL,8,Fwho is nominated for the regional
OL,9,FPride of Britain Fundraiser of the
OL,10,FYear award 2024.
OL,12,FA mother who dedicates her life to
OL,13,Ftackling knife crime after the murder
OL,14,Fof her brother has been nominated for
OL,15,Fa Pride of Britain award.
OL,17,FLaura Hughes, who lives in Formby, set
OL,18,Fup campaign charity kNOw Knife Crime
OL,19,Fin 2019, to mark what would have been
OL,20,Fher brother Colin McGinty's 40th
OL,21,Fbirthday.
