OL,3,CThe mum tackling knife-crime in
OL,4,Ccommunities after brother's murder
OL,6,FColin was just 21 when he was stabbed
OL,7,F15 times in a case of mistaken
OL,8,Fidentity after a night out in
OL,9,FLiverpool in 2001.
OL,11,FSince the charity was formed, Laura
OL,12,Fhas helped raise over #115,000 for
OL,13,Flife-saving bleeding control kits and
OL,14,Fcabinets, and carries out knife crime
OL,15,Fprevention work across the UK.
OL,17,FLaura hopes no-one needs to use these
OL,18,Fkits, but having them can and do save
OL,19,Flives.
