OL,3,CThe mum tackling knife-crime in
OL,4,Ccommunities after brother's murder
OL,6,F"What happened to Colin is happening
OL,7,Fmore and more", Laura said.
OL,9,F"Wherever you see anyone socialising,
OL,10,Fwe want to have equipment there and
OL,11,Fthat's why I'm going to keep going.
OL,13,F"I want Colin's name to be on people's
OL,14,Flips by getting the young kids to know
OL,15,Fthat knife crime isn't the norm.
OL,16,FThat's what scary because it is
OL,17,Fbecoming much more normalised."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
