OL,3,CThe mum tackling knife-crime in
OL,4,Ccommunities after brother's murder
OL,6,FIn 2019, having never run before,
OL,7,FLaura completed a marathon - the first
OL,8,Fof many fundraising missions for kNow
OL,9,FKnife Crime.
OL,11,FThis year, more than 16,000
OL,12,Fschoolchildren across Sefton took part
OL,13,Fin a running relay with bleed control
OL,14,Fkits as the baton, raising thousands
OL,15,Ffor more kits and cabinets to be
OL,16,Fplaced next to their classrooms.
OL,18,FLaura is among four finalists
OL,19,Fnominated for the Pride of Britain
OL,20,FRegional Fundraiser of the Year Award
OL,21,F2024 for the North West.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
