OL,3,CThe mum tackling knife-crime in
OL,4,Ccommunities after brother's murder
OL,6,F"I cannot believe that I have been
OL,7,Fnominated. I am completely over the
OL,8,Fmoon", she said.
OL,10,F"It would be the biggest motivator to
OL,11,Fkeep going. It's such a good accolade
OL,12,Fto have and makes what we're doing
OL,13,Fmore credible.
OL,15,F"The more people that are engaged with
OL,16,Fthe campaign, the more lives saved."
